  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/8006974/" class="title-link">游離個體</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-8006974"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/beausourire/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u115725861-10.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/beausourire/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">beausourire</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2016-07-25"
      class="main-meta">2016-07-25 04:37:29</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_8006974_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  從共同體中打散出來的個人，在先秦時代的看法中，是禍亂的根源，是“道術將為天下裂”。在現時代的人看來，是追求自由思想，文化蓬勃的軸心時代。然而歷史的來看，從共同體中打散出來的游離個體，事實上是秦漢帝國重組一元化新秩序的絕對必要條件。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
